raggable":true,"resizable":true,"contentEditable":true,"styleEditable":true,"text":"整体规划","placeholder":"","fontSize":41.59166666666667,"fontFamily":"FONT_54_16883828271116","fontId":54,"fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"normal","textDecoration":"","fill":"#000000","align":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeWidth":0,"stroke":"black","lineHeight":1.13,"letterSpacing":0,"backgroundEnabled":false,"backgroundColor":"transparent","backgroundOpacity":1,"backgroundCornerRadius":0.5,"backgroundPadding":0.5},{"id":"6rltlCJFtY","type":"text","name":"","opacity":1,"animations":[],"visible":true,"selectable":true,"removable":true,"alwaysOnTop":false,"showInExport":true,"x":135.884,"y":1337.347,"width":265.7,"height":48,"rotation":0,"blurEnabled":false,"blurRadius":10,"brightnessEnabled":false,"brightness":0,"sepiaEnabled":false,"grayscaleEnabled":false,"shadowEnabled":false,"shadowBlur":10,"shadowOffsetX":2,"shadowOffsetY":2,"shadowColor":"#5a5a5a","shadowOpacity":1,"draggable":true,"resizable":true,"contentEditable":true,"styleEditable":true,"text":"会籍顾问五名","placeholder":"","fontSize":41.59166666666667,"fontFamily":"FONT_54_16883828276758","fontId":54,"fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"normal","textDecoration":"","fill":"#000000","align":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeWidth":0,"stroke":"black","lineHeight":1.13,"letterSpacing":0,"backgroundEnabled":false,"backgroundColor":"transparent","backgroundOpacity":1,"backgroundCornerRadius":0.5,"backgroundPadding":0.5},{"id":"9gtfcCFPic","type":"text","name":"","opacity":1,"animations":[],"visible":true,"selectable":true,"removable":true,"alwaysOnTop":false,"showInExport":true,"x":97.1,"y":804.925,"width":1016.5,"height":414,"rotation":0,"blurEnabled":false,"blurRadius":10,"brightnessEnabled":false,"brightness":0,"sepiaEnabled":false,"grayscaleEnabled":false,"shadowEnabled":false,"shadowBlur":10,"shadowOffsetX":2,"shadowOffsetY":2,"shadowColor":"#5a5a5a","shadowOpacity":1,"draggable":true,"resizable":true,"contentEditable":true,"styleEditable":true,"text":"1、要有良好的身材体型，具备专业知识、技能\n\n2、具备一定的沟通能力、销售能力\n\n3、积极向上充满正能量\n\n4、拥有健身教练国家职业资格证书\n\n5、健身教练必须要掌握相关的专业知识和技能\n比如：运动解剖学、运动生理学、运动生物力学、运动损伤康复学等","placeholder":"","fontSize":33.541666666666664,"fontFamily":"FONT_220_168855435003952","fontId":220,"fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"normal","textDecoration":"","fill":"#000000","align":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeWidth":0,"stroke":"black","lineHeight":1.2299999999999998,"letterSpacing":0,"backgroundEnabled":false,"backgroundColor":"transparent","backgroundOpacity":1,"backgroundCornerRadius":0.5,"backgroundPadding":0.5},{"id":"5MI8NhGXDz","type":"text","name":"","opacity":1,"animations":[],"visible":true,"selectable":true,"removable":true,"alwaysOnTop":false,"showInExport":true,"x":97.1,"y":1398.925,"width":969.5,"height":418,"rotation":0,"blurEnabled":false,"blurRadius":10,"brightnessEnabled":false,"brightness":0,"sepiaEnabled":false,"grayscaleEnabled":false,"shadowEnabled":false,"shadowBlur":10,"shadowOffsetX":2,"shadowOffsetY":2,"shadowColor":"#5a5a5a","shadowOpacity":1,"draggable":true,"resizable":true,"contentEditable":true,"styleEditable":true,"text":"1、会籍顾问工作职位涉及会员管理和市场营销两个方面\n\n2、会籍顾问需帮助会员协调教练指导,督促会员坚持锻炼\n\n3、为企业提供销售收入\n\n4、电话联系以往咨询电话整理后排出的意向会员，作进一步沟通\n\n5、遵守俱乐部中和本部门的销售流程及有关规章制度\n服从管理，积极维护俱乐部形象\n","placeholder":"","fontSize":33.541666666666664,"fontFamily":"FONT_220_168855438206067","fontId":220,"fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"normal","textDecoration":"","fill":"#000000","align":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeWidth":0,"stroke":"black","lineHeight":1.13,"letterSpacing":0,"backgroundEnabled":false,"backgroundColor":"transparent","backgroundOpacity":1,"backgroundCornerRadius":0.5,"backgroundPadding":0.5},{"id":"U4fHPtzGSI","type":"text","name":"","opacity":1,"animations":[],"visible":true,"selectable":true,"removable":true,"alwaysOnTop":false,"showInExport":true,"x":97.1,"y":2217.925,"width":1023.5,"height":191,"rotation":0,"blurEnabled":false,"blurRadius":10,"brightnessEnabled":false,"brightness":0,"sepiaEnabled":false,"grayscaleEnabled":false,"shadowEnabled":false,"shadowBlur":10,"shadowOffsetX":2,"shadowOffsetY":2,"shadowColor":"#5a5a5a","shadowOpacity":1,"draggable":true,"resizable":true,"contentEditable":true,"styleEditable":true,"text":"健身运动是通过采用专门的方法和器械进行身体锻炼增强人们身体素\r质。专业人员配备 应该配备健康管理师、健身教练。专业设备配置应\r该配置运动监测与亚健康检测仪,音响设备。场地设置 可设置为普通\r顾客训练场地(设专门休息室,注意环境幽雅、安静）\r\r","placeholder":"","fontSize":33.541666666666664,"fontFamily":"FONT_220_16883828276987","fontId":220,"fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"normal","textDecoration":"","fill":"#000000","align":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeWidth":0,"stroke":"black","lineHeight":1.13,"letterSpacing":0,"backgroundEnabled":false,"backgroundColor":"transparent","backgroundOpacity":1,"backgroundCornerRadius":0.5,"backgroundPadding":0.5},{"id":"jKDhUUUGzS","type":"text","name":"","opacity":1,"animations":[],"visible":true,"selectable":true,"removable":true,"alwaysOnTop":false,"showInExport":true,"x":310.1,"y":2725.425,"width":321.5,"height":39,"rotation":0,"blurEnabled":false,"blurRadius":10,"brightnessEnabled":false,"brightness":0,"sepiaEnabled":false,"grayscaleEnabled":false,"shadowEnabled":false,"shadowBlur":10,"shadowOffsetX":2,"shadowOffsetY":2,"shadowColor":"#5a5a5a","shadowOpacity":1,"draggable":true,"resizable":true,"contentEditable":true,"styleEditable":true,"text":"电话：15213831908","placeholder":"","fontSize":33.541666666666664,"fontFamily":"FONT_220_16883828278663","fontId":220,"fontStyle":"normal","fontWeight":"normal","textDecoration":"","fill":"#000000","align":"left","verticalAlign":"top","strokeWidth":0,"stroke":"black","lineHeight":1.13,"letterSpacing":0,"backgroundEnabled":false,"backgroundColor":"transparent","backgroundOpacity":1,"backgroundCornerRadius":0.5,"backgroundPadding":0.5},{"id":"ieJTrU7fdr","type":"text","name":"","opacity":1,"animations":[],"visible":true,"selectable":true,"removable":true,"alwaysOnTop":false,"showInExport":true,"x":308.1,"y":2787.425,"width":475.5,"height